{"tha-ap484:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap484:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap484:0.3":"Buddhasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap484:1.1":"“Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap484:1.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap484:1.3":"Lakkhane itihase ca, ","tha-ap484:1.4":"sanighandusaketubhe. ","tha-ap484:2.1":"Nadisotapatibhaga, ","tha-ap484:2.2":"sissa ayanti me tada; ","tha-ap484:2.3":"Tesaham mante vacemi, ","tha-ap484:2.4":"rattindivamatandito. ","tha-ap484:3.1":"Siddhattho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap484:3.2":"loke uppajji tavade; ","tha-ap484:3.3":"Tamandhakaram nasetva, ","tha-ap484:3.4":"nanalokam pavattayi. ","tha-ap484:4.1":"Mama annataro sisso, ","tha-ap484:4.2":"sissanam so kathesi me; ","tha-ap484:4.3":"Sutvana te etamattham, ","tha-ap484:4.4":"arocesum mamam tada. ","tha-ap484:5.1":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap484:5.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap484:5.3":"Tassanuvattati jano, ","tha-ap484:5.4":"labho amham na vijjati. ","tha-ap484:6.1":"Adhiccuppattika buddha, ","tha-ap484:6.2":"cakkhumanto mahayasa; ","tha-ap484:6.3":"Yannunaham buddhasettham, ","tha-ap484:6.4":"passeyyam lokanayakam’. ","tha-ap484:7.1":"Ajinam me gahetvana, ","tha-ap484:7.2":"vakaciram kamandalum; ","tha-ap484:7.3":"Assama abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap484:7.4":"sisse amantayim aham. ","tha-ap484:8.1":"Odumbarikapupphamva, ","tha-ap484:8.2":"candamhi sasakam yatha; ","tha-ap484:8.3":"Vayasanam yatha khiram, ","tha-ap484:8.4":"dullabho lokanayako. ","tha-ap484:9.1":"Buddho lokamhi uppanno, ","tha-ap484:9.2":"manussattampi dullabham; ","tha-ap484:9.3":"Ubhosu vijjamanesu, ","tha-ap484:9.4":"savananca sudullabham. ","tha-ap484:10.1":"Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap484:10.2":"cakkhum lacchama no bhavam; ","tha-ap484:10.3":"Etha sabbe gamissama, ","tha-ap484:10.4":"sammasambuddhasantikam. ","tha-ap484:11.1":"Kamandaludhara sabbe, ","tha-ap484:11.2":"kharajinanivasino; ","tha-ap484:11.3":"Te jata bharabharita, ","tha-ap484:11.4":"nikkhamum vipina tada. ","tha-ap484:12.1":"Yugamattam pekkhamana, ","tha-ap484:12.2":"uttamattham gavesino; ","tha-ap484:12.3":"Asattidosarahita, ","tha-ap484:12.4":"asambhitava kesari. ","tha-ap484:13.1":"Appakicca aloluppa, ","tha-ap484:13.2":"nipaka santavuttino; ","tha-ap484:13.3":"Unchaya caramana te, ","tha-ap484:13.4":"buddhasetthamupagamum. ","tha-ap484:14.1":"Diyaddhayojane sese, ","tha-ap484:14.2":"byadhi me upapajjatha; ","tha-ap484:14.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap484:14.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap484:15.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap484:15.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap484:15.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap484:15.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap484:16.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap484:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap484:16.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap484:17.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap484:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap484:17.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap484:18.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap484:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap484:18.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap484:19.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma buddhasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap484:20.1":"Buddhasannakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}